### 891.

### A METHOD OF SEEING THE SUN ECLIPSED WITHOUT PAIN TO THE EYE.

<span id="img_v215301"></span> ![](img/v215301.jpg)

Take a piece of paper and pierce holes in it with a needle, and look at
the sun through these holes.

